WEBVTT

00:00:08.843 --> 00:00:11.011
Devious minds think alike.

00:00:13.097 --> 00:00:14.597
Don't go.

00:00:16.308 --> 00:00:17.976
l'll be quiet and just...

00:00:19.437 --> 00:00:20.770
lt's nice to

00:00:21.355 --> 00:00:23.565
just sit and smoke with somebody.

00:00:29.655 --> 00:00:31.322
Were you on that plane?

00:00:32.491 --> 00:00:33.825
Yeah, l was.

00:00:34.243 --> 00:00:35.285
You?

00:00:36.620 --> 00:00:38.621
You must have been sitting at the back.

